<h2 class="govuk-heading-m">What to do next</h2>
<p>You need to:</p>
<ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet">
  <li>design a 2-year programme of support and training that covers every ‘learn that’ and ‘learn how to’ statement in
    the
    <%= govuk_link_to("early career framework (ECF) (opens in new tab)", "https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/early-career-framework") %>
  <li>contact your appropriate body to find out what evidence is needed to demonstrate that your programme:
    <ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet">
      <li>is based on the ECF</li>
      <li>meets the statutory requirements</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
</ul>
<p>You do not need to add information about your ECTs and mentors to this service.</p>
<p>
  <%= govuk_link_to("See our statutory guidance (open in new tab)", "https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/early-career-framework-reforms-overview/early-career-framework-reforms-overview#schools-designing-and-delivering-their-own-ecf-based-induction") %>
  for information about funding, time off timetable, and roles.
</p>
